עמוד 11: מעבר במוריה
כותרת: "Journey through Moria"
תוכן: "Inside Moria, you face many challenges and discover the tomb of Balin."
משימה: "Find clues to solve the mystery of Balin's fate and avoid traps."
כפתור: "Continue to the Bridge of Khazad-dûm".
עמוד 12: גשר קאזאד-דום
כותרת: "The Bridge of Khazad-dûm"
תוכן: "You reach the Bridge of Khazad-dûm and encounter the Balrog."
משימה: "Help Gandalf defeat the Balrog by solving a series of quick puzzles."
כפתור: "Escape to Lothlórien".
עמוד 13: לות'לוריין
כותרת: "Arrival at Lothlórien"
תוכן: "Welcome to Lothlórien, the enchanted forest of the Elves."
משימה: "Answer questions about the history and lore of Lothlórien to gain the trust of Galadriel."
כפתור: "Receive the gifts from Galadriel".
עמוד 14: מתנות גלדריאל
כותרת: "Gifts from Galadriel"
תוכן: "Galadriel gives you gifts that will aid you in your journey."
משימה: "Identify and match the gifts to their descriptions."
כפתור: "Prepare for the journey to Amon Hen".
עמוד 15: אמון הן
כותרת: "The Hill of Amon Hen"
תוכן: "You reach Amon Hen and must defend yourself from orc attacks."
משימה: "Use the environment to set traps and solve puzzles to fend off the orcs."
כפתור: "Continue to Parth Galen".
עמוד 16: פרת גלן
כותרת: "The Breaking of the Fellowship"
תוכן: "The Fellowship is broken and you must decide your next steps."
משימה: "Choose a path and solve the riddles to find your way."
כפתור: "Help Frodo and Sam escape."
עמוד 17: בריחה עם פרודו וסאם
כותרת: "Escape with Frodo and Sam"
תוכן: "Help Frodo and Sam escape from the orcs and continue their journey."
משימה: "Navigate through a maze and avoid traps to reach safety."
כפתור: "Finish the adventure".
עמוד 18: סיום ההרפתקה
כותרת: "End of the Adventure"
תוכן: "Reflect on your journey and the adventures you've had."
משימה: "Review your choices and see how they impacted the story."
כפתור: "Receive your digital achievement certificate".
